<section class="page-header">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">Gateway Trust</p>
    <h1>BlackGate Gateway</h1>
    <p>O gateway opera em modo operator-mediated para verificações de compatibilidade contra upstreams internos selecionados.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="header-badge">
    <span>Status</span>
    <strong>review required</strong>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="dashboard-grid">
  <article class="panel">
    <div class="panel-head">
      <h2>Gateway metadata</h2>
      <a href="/api/operator/gateway-metadata">/api/operator/gateway-metadata</a>
    </div>
    <p class="muted-copy">Operator context enables compatibility checks against selected upstreams. O endpoint de metadata informa os hosts permitidos e o formato do gateway fetch.</p>
    <p class="muted-copy">Selected upstreams expose health and metadata only through operator-mediated gateway checks.</p>
  </article>

  <article class="panel">
    <div class="panel-head">
      <h2>Health probe</h2>
      <span class="subtle">example</span>
    </div>
    <div class="kv-list">
      <div><span>Endpoint</span><strong>/api/operator/gateway-fetch</strong></div>
      <div><span>Example</span><strong>api-core.internal/health</strong></div>
      <div><span>Mode</span><strong>simulated internal resolver</strong></div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="panel wide">
    <div class="panel-head">
      <h2>Allowed upstreams</h2>
      <span class="subtle">training map</span>
    </div>
    <div class="compact-list">
      <% allowedHosts.forEach((host) => { %>
        <div class="list-row">
          <div>
            <strong><%= host %></strong>
            <span>Internal service simulation. No external network request is performed.</span>
          </div>
          <span class="badge status-watch">internal</span>
        </div>
      <% }) %>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
